{"tid":915922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不斷更新● 九西補選】投票率仍低5選1分散票源 李卓人「極度告急」","createTime":"2018-11-25T10:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T05:45:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6eacca3f331f1989a486df47ef0bc5220388b1d9","tid":915922,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T10:31:07.000Z","msg":"2018年11月25日 <br />\n<br />\n【不斷更新● 九西補選】投票率仍低5選1分散票源 李卓人「極度告急」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後更新: 1125 17:34 /\t建立時間 (HKT): 1125 00:01<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日九西補選投票，港人要用選票守護香港。今次補選候選人有伍廸希、曾麗文、李卓人、馮檢基、陳凱欣，而劉小麗則被裁定提名無效，無法參選。今日各區票站位置︰ <a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/legco2018kwby/chi/p_cs.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Flegco2018kwby%2Fchi%2Fp_cs.html&d=MGac5UhZSEeZHHCKI2XDkYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=f917c7b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/legco2018kwby/chi/p_cs.html</a> 。<br />\n<br />\n【17:20】李卓人表示，投票率雖與311補選時相若，但今次有5個候選人，除陳凱欣外，亦另有3名候選人，強調投票率要過50%自己才有勝算，現時形勢非常非常緊急，呼籲選民踴躍投票，勿因天雨而不投票。他又表示黃埔和美孚的投票率偏低，故未來數小時會繼續呼籲選民投票。<br />\n<br />\n【16:24】李卓人指，目前選情「非常非常緊急」，每一票都很重要，又指留意到很多長者在老人院，被建制派推出來作掌心雷式投票，呼籲巿民為自由、民生和香港，必須要投票。 <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PRYlPH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PRYlPH&d=MGac5UhZSEeZHHCKI2XDkYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=46de2043\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2PRYlPH</a> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PRY5jH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PRY5jH&d=MGac5UhZSEeZHHCKI2XDkYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=724e6f50\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2PRY5jH</a> <br />\n<br />\n國泰空中服務員工會副主席黎玉嬋表示，有工會成員今日收到冒認工會的電話呼籲會員投票支持陳凱欣，黎指工會一向只支持李卓人，批評有人冒認工會拉票的做法可恥。<br />\n【15:36】民主派會議召集人毛孟靜、民主派議員區諾軒今午3時，在西九龍中心外為民主派候選人李卓人拉票，其間高舉「極度告急，贏定輸，只差你一票」的巨型標語。李卓人形容目前投票率偏低，選情告急，希望大家為未來投票支持三號，令立法會不再被建制派壟斷，高喊「拒絕香港大陸化，拒絕政府倒錢落海！」口號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李卓人將於下午5時會見傳媒，屆時《蘋果》將會直播<br />\n《蘋果》YouTube <br />\n《蘋果》Facebook <br />\n《蘋果》動直擊"},{"pid":"87239a47fed5c65b01d0262d497bfed892e3d4e5","tid":915922,"uid":143241,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"條垃圾尋日都告急緊喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac43cef1270f319d8fb20bccc869ef4b47288cd","tid":915922,"uid":136431,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T10:32:15.000Z","msg":"幾時出特急同超特急？"},{"pid":"1de02dbf12ca86e54dc0ec9828175c382acb2988","tid":915922,"uid":139700,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T10:38:30.000Z","msg":"一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而竭，吹咗廿幾年啲人仲含撚嘅?"},{"pid":"06951d9c1c31b30e8bdfd79b0ac614bf45563632","tid":915922,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"急屎？"},{"pid":"ba4a419c8d14de965d392997ea8f1671852e74a8","tid":915922,"uid":129878,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"87239a47fed5c65b01d0262d497bfed892e3d4e5","tid":915922,"uid":143241,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"條垃圾尋日都告急緊喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T12:12:04.000Z","msg":"你重垃圾, 垃圾5毛狗"},{"pid":"57de78c884c6eaeeb3f3b8d7998c091bf0fd4501","tid":915922,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T12:13:27.000Z","msg":"理桌人"},{"pid":"10a720f58c557fd9db674661ef0375fefcad19b1","tid":915922,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba4a419c8d14de965d392997ea8f1671852e74a8","tid":915922,"uid":129878,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"87239a47fed5c65b01d0262d497bfed892e3d4e5","tid":915922,"uid":143241,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T10:32:03.000Z","msg":"條垃圾尋日都告急緊喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T12:12:04.000Z","msg":"你重垃圾, 垃圾5毛狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-25T12:13:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母你侮辱我！五你老母啊仆你個臭街！<img src=\"/ass